metadata.Plot: Experiencing cold feet about his upcoming arranged royal wedding, a charming European prince steals away incognito to the U.S. in search of true love. Pretending to be someone he isn't, the prince-on-the-lam meets Emma a diner waitress whose Christmas needs considerable brightening.
metadata.Writer: Peter Sullivan, Jeffrey Schenck, Fred Olen Ray
metadata.Actors: Viva Bianca, Kirk Barker, Aaron O'Connell
